metadata.name: North America Nebula
metadata.description:
This bidders edition went with New Beginnings on Foundation.

This is a DSLR and lens image of North America Nebula and Pelican Nebula taken with my small rig while the primary rig collected light for New Beginnings.

Taken from beautiful dark skies this shows the countless stars in this area which is directly in the Milky Way arm.

48x30s stacked with full calibration in APP, processed in PS

Canon EF L 70-200mm f/2.8 @ 200mm, f/3.5  
Canon 6D ISO2500  
SkyWatcher Star Adventurer

Imaged in Bortle 3 skies in Northumberland, England
